  "detailed_description": "Touch the Oriental Wisdom from the ancient sage himself and build him a town! <br><strong>!!!!We’ve decided to significantly refresh this series of games, so the game mechanics of this game has lots of changes, including a power-up system and some new mechanics which you’ve never seen in our games before.</strong><br>As usual, there’s also some bonus games: Blocks, Mahjongs, Spot the difference and Hidden Object scenes. And you can replay your favorite levels!<br>And, of course, there's a town to build!",
